Kent born, London based, DJ & Producer Tim Green makes his Essential Mix debut. He's best known for his releases on labels Dirtybird, Cocoon and Get Physical. He regularly plays major clubs like Fabric in London and Circus in Liverpool and he is resident at a night called Bedlam in his home county.
